item.title: How to Contribute
item.description: hugo-enib Demo : https://shiny-kitten-777df7.netlify.app/ How to Contribute Fork the github repo Make some modifications Commit your modifications Open a pull request Run the portfolio locally To run the portfolio locally, you should have hugo installed. sudo snap install hugo Then, in the repository folder, run hugo server
